snippet.title: Miniature Garden English Opening
snippet.description:
"Miniature Garden", theme song to visual novel Miniature Garden, developed by Muzintou and localized by Fruitbat Factory.

Composition: Sugimoto Yoshinori
Arrangement: Murasame44 (Chain-sou)
Lyrics: Senca
Vocals: Kanade Nakoto (Lump of Sugar)

http://store.steampowered.com/app/494170
http://fruitbatfactory.com/miniature/
http://muzintou.sakura.ne.jp/
